{"tid":744942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發！]男子疑因家庭問題用滾油和通渠水潑向妻子","createTime":"2018-07-16T10:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T15:25:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"228fb967ef3d5c1aacf22d92dafa06ef37a46e33","tid":744942,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"2018-07-16 17:21<br />\n(澳門電台消息) 1名 40歲本澳男子懷疑因家庭問題與妻子爭執，用滾油和通渠水潑向對方，導致妻子身體多處 2至 3級燒傷，視力嚴重受損或至全盲，司警已將這名男子移送檢察院處理，他現時正被羈押。 案中夫婦於 2016年底感情轉差，妻子多次提出離婚要求，她於上週四晚再次提出離婚，兩人發生口角，丈夫先後以加熱的食用油和通渠水潑向在客廳的妻子，男子作案後沒有離開單位，事件由鄰居報警。 司警稱，案中 1名家傭由於曾被受害人擁抱，身體亦被腐蝕性液體波及，手腳亦被灼傷。這對夫婦育有 1名 6歲兒子，司警已通知社工局和教青局跟進。 (區賢達 雷翠雲)"},{"pid":"510e1502df8cc41b25c0b1b01139b9e614ef8cfa","tid":744942,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"擁抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b079931050d30b2679945465d5dd11607c942f","tid":744942,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb9cee72a93eb5d7124e105966e551d085ad97e","tid":744942,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d6ed3f0d3fdbe7dd42f1cad60c82c6a16ff1845","tid":744942,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"510e1502df8cc41b25c0b1b01139b9e614ef8cfa","tid":744942,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"擁抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"好主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d815e686bdef2cad5cd7fa974e7ffce823637315","tid":744942,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmo